---
title: Pesto Salmon en Croute with Honey Roasted Carrots and Baby Leaf Salad
description: This Pesto Salmon en Croute is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R32_W17_UK_SS13276-4_Main_high-c30e7493.jpg
